Cavaliers_football\", \"score\": 0.9250055030013099, \"rank\": 0.08105175381891688, \"text\": \"Virginia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why do you ask?\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is what you need to know about Wilson.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 16 years old, Wilson is one of the youngest members of the 2024 U.S. Olympic team across all sports and events.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He became the youngest American male track and field athlete in history when he punched his ticket to the Paris Olympics after he finished sixth at the U.S. Olympic Trials in Eugene, Oregon in the 400m.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_football\", \"score\": 0.9778523301629789, \"rank\": 0.022649038571560767, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the finals, he produced a 44.94 and from there, was selected for the 4x400m relay pool.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rising junior from Bullis School (MD) joins Hezlyn Rivera, a gymnast from New Jersey, as one of the two youngest competitors for Team USA.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bullis_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bullis School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bullis_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bullis_School\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"score\": 0.9978226978602002, \"rank\": 0.001639469423814553, \"text\": \"MD\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\"}, {\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999950427864039, \"rank\": 4.087476388902709e-06, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"score\": 0.7483867592786444, \"rank\": 0.3337913204232962, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.999723858259533, \"rank\": 0.00017696344161550377, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one thing to win a national title once and it's another to do it five times.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us be honest, Wilson knows how to win.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the AAU Junior Olympic Games, Wilson has been winning the 400m title since 2017.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1314, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only year where he did not defend his crown was in 2020 during the pandemic.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When he was nine years old, Wilson won the title in 1:02.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1475, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he was 14 years old, Wilson dropped his time to a 47.77, which was back in 2022.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This outdoor season alone, Wilson shattered the national high school record in the 400m.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not do it not once.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not twice.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But three times.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the prelims of the U.S. Olympic Trials, Wilson went 44.66 to break Darrell Robinson's 44.69 from 1982.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the semi-final round at the Olympic Trials, Wilson improved on that mark to a 44.59.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though these performances were jaw-dropping, what he did was Holloway Pro Classic was memorable.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9997131976412116, \"rank\": 0.000286829593661114, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Wilson toed the line at the University of Florida, he was able to hold his own against professional athletes including Matthew Boling and Bryce Deadmon.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"score\": 0.7603814162910995, \"rank\": 0.2795972712856902, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._J._Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 2161, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Boling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Boling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Boling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Boling\"}, {\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryce_Dessner\", \"score\": 0.9999989185563599, \"rank\": 7.997089929923032e-07, \"text\": \"Bryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryce_Dessner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryce_Dessner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilson crossed the finish line as the fastest 